data.title: Faith Builders Church
data.meta_description: Faith Builders Church Milwaukee is a non-denominational multicultural family church in Milwaukee, WI. With Pastors Jeffrey & Robin Pruitt. Looking for churches near you? Looking for churches in Milwaukee? Want an exciting church? Check us out!
data.text:
Welcome to your church

AS A MILWAUKEE CHURCH…

…our focus is Jesus, Milwaukee, and YOU. We are geared toward your family & we have a place for everyone! We are a multicultural + multi background + non-denominational church. We want you to know there is a place for everyone at Faith Builders Church! You can always expect engaging worship, real life teaching, authentic community, and a fun and safe environment for your kids. Whoever you are, and wherever you come from, we’re in this together & we hope you feel at home!

Help us Build Faith, Share Faith.
